snippet.title: Star Wars™: The Old Republic™ Galactic Starfighter Announcement "Conflict Rising" Trailer
snippet.description:
Watch the "Conflict Rising" trailer and take your battle to space with epic 12v12 dogfights in the new Free-to-Play Digital Expansion: Galactic Starfighter, coming to Star Wars™: The Old Republic™!

For more information, visit www.swtor.com/galactic-starfighter. 

PLAY FREE NOW: http://www.swtor.com/play-free
